OL,3,CI'd rather sit with the fans, says
OL,4,CJeff Stelling amid row with Hartlepool
OL,5,Cowner
OL,7,FBroadcaster Jeff Stelling has vowed to
OL,8,Fjoin Hartlepool fans on the terraces
OL,9,Famid an escalating row with the
OL,10,FNational League club's owner.
OL,12,FFormer Sky Sports and now TalkSPORT
OL,13,Fpresenter Stelling joked on Tuesday
OL,14,Fevening that he might have to dress up
OL,15,Fas a Blues Brother to support the club
OL,16,Fafter Raj Singh wrote to Pool's league
OL,17,Frivals urging them not to admit him to
OL,18,Ftheir boardrooms this season.
