OL,3,CI'd rather sit with the fans, says
OL,4,CJeff Stelling amid row with Hartlepool
OL,5,Cowner
OL,7,FThe 70-year-old stood down as honorary
OL,8,Fpresident in May in protest at the
OL,9,Fowner's handling of negotiations to
OL,10,Fsell Hartlepool to a local consortium
OL,11,Fafter talks had stalled, and while he
OL,12,Fbelieves he will not be welcome at the
OL,13,FPrestige Group Stadium, he will
OL,14,Fcontinue to support his team on the
OL,15,Froad.
