OL,3,CI'd rather sit with the fans, says
OL,4,CJeff Stelling amid row with Hartlepool
OL,5,Cowner
OL,7,FAsked about the situation on TalkSPORT
OL,8,Fon Wednesday (8 August), Stelling, who
OL,9,Frevealed he was asleep when the story
OL,10,Fbroke on Tuesday night, said: "You
OL,11,Fknow what? It didn't bother me, I'm
OL,12,Fnot president of the football club
OL,13,Fanymore.
OL,15,F"It's my football club, I'm a lifelong
OL,16,Fsupporter of that football club and if
OL,17,Fit came down to the fact that I
OL,18,Ftravelled and stood with the Poolies,
OL,19,Fthe Hartlepool supporters, wherever
OL,20,Fthey are, then that's...
