OL,3,CI'd rather sit with the fans, says
OL,4,CJeff Stelling amid row with Hartlepool
OL,5,Cowner
OL,7,F"I'd already bought my ticket ` we're
OL,8,Faway to Yeovil on Saturday ` I'd
OL,9,Falready bought my ticket to be with
OL,10,Fthe fans, so I didn't get the issue or
OL,11,Fwhy Mr Singh wanted to raise it."
OL,13,FHe continued: "But of course, then it
OL,14,Fwas leaked to the media and then of
OL,15,Fcourse it all spiralled and spiralled
OL,16,Fout of control. The other thing that I
OL,17,Ftook offence to was in the statement
OL,18,Fhe says in the unlikely event that I
OL,19,Fattend games independently.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@OOU
