OL,3,CI'd rather sit with the fans, says
OL,4,CJeff Stelling amid row with Hartlepool
OL,5,Cowner
OL,7,F"Well, I mean, last season I went to
OL,8,FAldershot, Eastleigh, Solihull,
OL,9,FSouthend, Sutton, Wealdstone, Woking,
OL,10,FDagenham and Redbridge, Ebbsfleet,
OL,11,FMaidenhead and a few others as well,
OL,12,Fso, it's not so unlikely that I'll
OL,13,Fattend."
OL,15,FIn his letter ` which was sent last
OL,16,Fmonth ` Singh wrote: "You may be aware
OL,17,Ffrom media coverage that Jeff Stelling
OL,18,Fhas resigned as honorary president of
OL,19,FHartlepool United Football Club.
