OL,3,CI'd rather sit with the fans, says
OL,4,CJeff Stelling amid row with Hartlepool
OL,5,Cowner
OL,7,F"As chairman of Hartlepool United
OL,8,FFootball Club, I would kindly and
OL,9,Fconsiderately ask that Mr Stelling is
OL,10,Fnot provided with official HUFC
OL,11,Fdignitary spaces in your boardroom or
OL,12,Fequivalent for any Hartlepool United
OL,13,Ffixture at your home ground.
OL,15,F"In the unlikely event that Mr
OL,16,FStelling independently attends any
OL,17,FHartlepool United fixture at your home
OL,18,Fground, I'd further request that you
OL,19,Fconsider to seat Mr Stelling
OL,20,Fseparately to any HUFC dignitaries or
OL,21,Fstaff."
