OL,3,CI'd rather sit with the fans, says
OL,4,CJeff Stelling amid row with Hartlepool
OL,5,Cowner
OL,7,FStelling, who confirmed he had
OL,8,Fintroduced the agent of Ryan Reynolds
OL,9,Fand Rob McElhenney to the club after
OL,10,Fthey had expressed an interest in
OL,11,Fbuying it before they opted to invest
OL,12,Fin Wrexham, has insisted he would be
OL,13,Fhappy to discuss the situation with
OL,14,FSingh.
OL,16,FHe said: "I haven't spoken to Mr Singh
OL,17,Ffor months ` it might even be a year `
OL,18,Fso this was just completely out of the
OL,19,Fblue. I just don't regard it as any
OL,20,Fbig deal.
