OL,3,CI'd rather sit with the fans, says
OL,4,CJeff Stelling amid row with Hartlepool
OL,5,Cowner
OL,7,F"I don't think I'd be welcome at home
OL,8,Fgames ` I'd probably have to go in
OL,9,Fdisguise ` but certainly at away
OL,10,Fgames, I'm very happy to go with the
OL,11,Ffans, no problem whatsoever. I'd
OL,12,Frather go with the fans, let's put it
OL,13,Fthat way.
OL,15,F"I'll be at Yeovil on Saturday and
OL,16,FI'll tell you what, I'll say it right
OL,17,Fnow ` if Mr Singh is there, I'll be
OL,18,Fhappy to meet him and have a chat with
OL,19,Fhim."
